              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/14411906/" class="">1.1 莫斯科与中国的苏维埃革命</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/tsukika/" class=" " title="Moonice">Moonice</a>
